        <updateDate>2020-10-29T13:00:28Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Addiction Treatment Access Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides for Medicare coverage of addiction counselor services that are used to diagnose and treat substance abuse and that would otherwise be covered if provided by a physician, including incidental services, as long as no payment is made to other providers for such services.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
